OL,3,CCivil service internships to be
OL,4,Crestricted to working class
OL,6,FThe government will tighten
OL,7,Feligibility criteria for Whitehall
OL,8,Finternships as part of a broader push
OL,9,Fto make the civil service more
OL,10,Frepresentative of the working class.
OL,12,FAccording to the BBC, the main
OL,13,Finternship scheme will now be limited
OL,14,Fto students from "lower socio-economic
OL,15,Fbackgrounds".
OL,17,FPat McFadden, the Chancellor of the
OL,18,FDuchy of Lancaster and the minister
OL,19,Fresponsible for civil service reform,
OL,20,Fsaid that Whitehall needed to reflect
OL,21,Fthe broader community.
