OL,3,CCivil service internships to be
OL,4,Crestricted to working class
OL,6,F"We need to get more working-class
OL,7,Fyoung people into the Civil Service so
OL,8,Fit harnesses the broadest range of
OL,9,Ftalent and truly reflects the
OL,10,Fcountry," he told the BBC.
OL,12,F"Government makes better decisions
OL,13,Fwhen it represents and understands the
OL,14,Fpeople we serve."
OL,16,FThe changes are expected to take
OL,17,Feffect from summer 2026 and will give
OL,18,Fyoung people experience writing
OL,19,Fbriefings, planning events, conducting
OL,20,Fpolicy research and shadowing civil
OL,21,Fservants, according to the broadcaster.
