OL,3,CCivil service internships to be
OL,4,Crestricted to working class
OL,6,FThe existing work summer placement
OL,7,Fprogramme, which lasts up to eight
OL,8,Fweeks and is paid, is open to
OL,9,Fundergraduates in the final two years
OL,10,Fof their degree.
OL,12,FThe Duchy of Lancaster has been
OL,13,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,15,FThe move comes after the Government
OL,16,Fannounced plans to move thousands more
OL,17,Fcivil servants out of London as part
OL,18,Fof plans to "radically reform the
OL,19,Fstate".
