OL,3,CCivil service internships to be
OL,4,Crestricted to working class
OL,6,FIn May, the Government confirmed it
OL,7,Fwould cut the number of civil servants
OL,8,Fworking in London by 12,000 and shift
OL,9,Fjobs to a series of new regional
OL,10,F"campuses" across the country.
OL,12,FMr McFadden said at the time that the
OL,13,FGovernment would be relocating a
OL,14,F"substantial number of roles".
OL,16,F"The aim is to reduce the London count
OL,17,Fby about 12,000. That will save us #94
OL,18,Fmillion in lease costs because the
OL,19,Fproperties in London are very
OL,20,Fexpensive.
