OL,6,F"And we will move thousands ` it's
OL,7,Fdifficult to put a precise number `
OL,8,Fthousands of those jobs to new themed
OL,9,Fcampuses around the country," he told
OL,10,FTimes Radio.
OL,12,FThe changes will also see 11
OL,13,FGovernment office buildings in London
OL,14,Fclose, including one of its largest
OL,15,FWestminster sites, in a move expected
OL,16,Fto save #94 million a year by 2032.
OL,18,FThe move will see two new major
OL,19,F"campuses" created, one in Manchester
OL,20,Ffocused on digital innovation and AI
OL,21,Fand another in Aberdeen on energy.
