OL,6,FManchester is already home to major
OL,7,Foffices of the science and culture
OL,8,Fdepartments, while Aberdeen houses the
OL,9,Fnew Great British Energy headquarters.
OL,11,FOther roles will be created in
OL,12,FBirmingham, Leeds, Cardiff, Glasgow,
OL,13,FDarlington, Newcastle and Tyneside,
OL,14,FSheffield, Bristol, Edinburgh, Belfast
OL,15,Fand York, with the changes expected to
OL,16,Fbring #729 million to the local
OL,17,Feconomy by 2030.
